org.jpac.plc
Class ReadRequest

java.lang.Object
  org.jpac.plc.Request
      org.jpac.plc.ReadRequest

public abstract class ReadRequest
extends Request

represents a read request. Can be added to a an instance of ReadMultipleData and will contain the data supplied by the plc on return.
